OL,6,FPam began running Barkham's Post
OL,7,FOffice in 1987. However trouble
OL,8,Fstarted with the Horizon IT system
OL,9,Fwhen she moved her Post Office into a
OL,10,Ftemporary portakabin in 2009 while a
OL,11,Fnew building was constructed.
OL,13,FIn October that year the system showed
OL,14,Fshe was #388 down, so she paid with
OL,15,Fher own cash, assured by the helpline
OL,16,Fit was to do with the move.
OL,18,FPam said: "When I got to the next
OL,19,Ftrading period - it didn't appear that
OL,20,Fanything was wrong.
