OL,6,F"Certainly everything seemed to work
OL,7,Fon the terminal, but the next trading
OL,8,Fstatement seemed to show me #2,500
OL,9,Fdown.
OL,11,F"When I did my next trading statement
OL,12,Fon January 6th, a dreadful day I'll
OL,13,Fnever forget that one, I was #9,500
OL,14,Fdown.
OL,16,F"We were in a portakabin; a tin can on
OL,17,Fthe side of the road. I was so careful
OL,18,Fwith every bit of money and I just
OL,19,Ffreaked out."
