OL,6,FConcerns were raised by her line
OL,7,Fmanager, but knowing she recorded
OL,8,Fevery transaction on paper, Pam stood
OL,9,Fher ground. She said she was not going
OL,10,Fto be accused of stealing thousands.
OL,12,F"I said 'This is just nonsense, this
OL,13,Fis something to do with the Horizon
OL,14,Fsystem' and he just said, 'Oh well
OL,15,Fmany people have said that but nobody
OL,16,Fhas ever been able to prove it'.
