OL,6,F"And I said, 'Okay fine. Give me your
OL,7,Fback office data, I'll compare it with
OL,8,Fmy transaction logs. But if you really
OL,9,Fthink I've stolen this money, send the
OL,10,Fpolice round, they can arrest me, and
OL,11,FI'll see you in court with all my
OL,12,Fevidence'."
OL,14,FAudits were carried out and phone
OL,15,Fcalls were had, but in 2010 she was
OL,16,Fsuspended without notice.
