OL,6,FShe said: "I came out the next morning
OL,7,Fat half past eight and opened up the
OL,8,Fpost office - and my second auditor
OL,9,Fturned up and he said 'I'm here to do
OL,10,Fan audit'.
OL,12,F"I said 'another one? Why?' and he
OL,13,Fsaid, 'well this one is a closing
OL,14,Faudit'.
OL,16,F"And that was the first I knew about
OL,17,Fit. I couldn't speak to the auditor I
OL,18,Fhad never been so angry... and then he
OL,19,Ftook the keys away."
