OL,6,FPam sold newspapers and milk in the
OL,7,Fshop in order to make ends meet, but
OL,8,Ffor years lived in fear she would be
OL,9,Farrested.
OL,11,FWhile she says she is glad Fujitsu,
OL,12,Fthe company behind Horizon, , Pam
OL,13,Fwants more responsibility to be taken
OL,14,Fby the Post Office for what she, and
OL,15,Fmore than 700 others, have suffered.
OL,17,FShe said: "They have destroyed lives.
OL,18,FThey've ruined marriages, they've
OL,19,Fruined families. And yet no one at the
OL,20,Fpost office is being held responsible
OL,21,Fin any way at all.
